## Phase 2: Component Overhaul

### Step 2.1: Buttons
**Find**: All button components/styles
**Replace with**: New button system

```css
/* Base button */
.btn {
  font-family: var(--font-primary);
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
  padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.15s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}

/* Primary - Gradient (intentional) */
.btn-primary {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-from), var(--accent-to));
  color: white;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  border: none;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.btn-primary:active {
  transform: scale(0.98);
}

/* Secondary - Outline */
.btn-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  border-color: var(--border-medium);
}

.btn-secondary:hover {
  border-color: var(--border-strong);
  background: var(--bg-secondary);
}

/* Ghost - Minimal */
.btn-ghost {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  border: none;
}

.btn-ghost:hover {
  background: var(--bg-secondary);
  color: var(--text-primary);
}

/* Sizes */
.btn-sm {
  padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
  font-size: var(--text-xs);
}

.btn-lg {
  padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-8);
  font-size: var(--text-base);
}
```

**React/Component example**:
```jsx
// Before (generic SaaS)
<button className="bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 rounded-lg px-4 py-2">
  Click me
</button>

// After (Offerloop style)
<button className="btn btn-primary">
  Click me
</button>
```

### Step 2.2: Cards → Lists
**CRITICAL**: Remove ALL card components. Replace with Linear-style lists.

**Before** (Delete this pattern):
```jsx
<div className="card bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6">
  <h3>Contact Name</h3>
  <p>Details...</p>
</div>
```

**After** (Use this pattern):
```jsx
<div className="list-container">
  <div className="list-item">
    <h3>Contact Name</h3>
    <p>Details...</p>
  </div>
  <div className="list-item">
    <h3>Another Contact</h3>
    <p>More details...</p>
  </div>
</div>
```

**Styles**:
```css
.list-container {
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  overflow: hidden;
  background: var(--bg-primary);
}

.list-item {
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  transition: background 0.1s ease;
}

.list-item:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.list-item:hover {
  background: var(--bg-secondary);
}

.list-item-interactive {
  cursor: pointer;
}

.list-item-interactive:hover {
  background: var(--accent-soft);
}
```

### Step 2.3: Forms & Inputs
**Find**: All input, textarea, select elements

```css
.input {
  font-family: var(--font-primary);
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-medium);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  background: var(--bg-primary);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  transition: all 0.15s ease;
  width: 100%;
}

.input:focus {
  outline: none;
  border-color: var(--accent-solid);
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-soft);
}

.input::placeholder {
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
}

.input:disabled {
  background: var(--bg-tertiary);
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  cursor: not-allowed;
}

/* Error state */
.input-error {
  border-color: #EF4444;
}

.input-error:focus {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
}
```

