## Important Notes

### DO NOT TOUCH
- Firebase authentication logic
- API integrations (PDL, OpenAI, Stripe)
- Database queries
- Backend routes
- Email generation logic
- Credit calculation logic
- Payment processing

### SAFE TO MODIFY
- All CSS/styles
- Component markup (as long as functionality preserved)
- Class names (update consistently)
- Visual hierarchy
- Spacing and layout
- Typography
- Colors
- Animations

### If Something Breaks
1. Check browser console for errors
2. Verify API calls still work
3. Test authentication flow
4. Check form submissions
5. Rollback specific file if needed

